sequenceDiagram

actor User as Członek
participant UI as Frontend / Panel
participant PinService as PinCatalogService
participant DB as Database
participant OrderService as OrderService
participant Pricing as PricingEngine

%% =========================
%% 1. OPEN PIN CATALOG
%% =========================
User ->> UI: Otwiera "Piny belgijskie"
UI ->> PinService: getAvailablePins()
PinService ->> DB: SELECT * FROM Pin WHERE active = true
DB -->> PinService: Lista pinów
PinService -->> UI: Available pins
UI -->> User: Wyświetla katalog

%% =========================
%% 2. SELECT PRODUCTS
%% =========================
User ->> UI: Wybiera piny + ilości
UI ->> OrderService: createDraftOrder(items)

%% =========================
%% 3. PRICE CALCULATION
%% =========================
OrderService ->> PinService: getPinDetails(pin_ids)
PinService ->> DB: Fetch pin prices
DB -->> PinService: Pin data
PinService -->> OrderService: Pricing data

OrderService ->> Pricing: calculateTotal(items, prices)
Pricing -->> OrderService: total_cost

OrderService -->> UI: Draft order + total_cost
UI -->> User: Wyświetla podsumowanie

%% =========================
%% 4. ORDER CONFIRMATION
%% =========================
User ->> UI: Zatwierdza zamówienie
UI ->> OrderService: submitOrder()

OrderService ->> DB: Save Order
OrderService ->> DB: Save OrderItems
DB -->> OrderService: Order persisted

OrderService -->> UI: Order confirmed
UI -->> User: Potwierdzenie zamówienia

%% =========================
%% ALT FLOW
%% =========================
alt Brak dostępnych pinów
    PinService -->> UI: Empty list
    UI -->> User: Komunikat "Brak pinów"
end